UID:032ce04b-0afd-495f-9660-09b9789676aa@travel-concierge
DESCRIPTION:**Day 1 — Arrival in Paradise**\n- 07:30 Breakfast: Artjuna 
 Café — try their signature pancakes\, ~₹250/person\n- 09:30 Morning: 
 Fort Aguada (open 09:30–18:00\, entry ₹50) — a 17th-century Portugue
 se fort offering breathtaking views of the Arabian Sea\n  → Transport: H
 ire a shared taxi from Goa International Airport (Dabolim) to Fort Aguada\
 , ~₹800 for 3 people\, 45 minutes\n- 13:00 Lunch: Sublime Restaurant —
  recommended: their veggie burgers\, ~₹400/person\n- 15:00 Afternoon: Ca
 langute Beach — relax and soak up the sun on one of Goa's most popular b
 eaches\n  → Transport: Walk from Sublime Restaurant to Calangute Beach\,
  10 minutes\n- 19:00 Sunset: Calangute Beach — watch the sunset over the
  Arabian Sea\n- 20:00 Dinner: Infantaria Restaurant — must-try: their ve
 ggie pizza\, ~₹500/person\n- Local tip: Visit the local market near Cala
 ngute Beach to buy souvenirs and try some street food\n- Indoor backup: Vi
 sit the Deltin Royale Casino\, a luxurious casino with various games and e
 ntertainment options\n- Group tip: When travelling in a group\, it's essen
 tial to book accommodations and restaurants in advance to ensure availabil
 ity and to get the best deals
END:VEVENT
